Collie,

I would think more like the auto tranny needs new fluid or some sort of 
adjustment.  Sounds like the torque converter is trying to engage before 
you are ready....don't know much about vw auto tranny tho.

Maybe replace any vacuum tubing to the tranny controls first?

Cheers, dave


